Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（本片开始）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气真好啊 好热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天啊 因为很久不见了 很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和好美开始交往一个月……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超有趣的 在电影院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有爆米花的味道 很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 为什么僵尸那么可爱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说如此 为什么僵尸那么可爱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好喜欢僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好喜欢僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要一直看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人公 不是有一次……吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 想说都没人在的……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要丢鸡蛋了的话 变成僵尸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吓一跳吧？好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一段内容你有好好记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有看了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像最近因为工作很忙的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说压力很大的 有点担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题？那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题？那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说今天因为工作很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点回去不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐的时光过的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 可以去你家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次邀请好美来家里……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么房间呀？太脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 叫女友来家里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是该先打扫干净点的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法 一起帮你整理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起待在这个房间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 老是吃这种东西对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不年轻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法 我来一起住 照顾你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也能帮你煮饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能分担房租
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去大学也很近呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起住！？……和好美同居！？……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 好像说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很困扰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 快乐时间一下子就过完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同居吧 西宫好美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那起几个礼拜后…… 和好美的同居的开始了……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李都搬完了吧 好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新沙发啊 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀都疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好软啊 这沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来两人一起住的 很令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要那个电子烤箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的话就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我因为最爱做点心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是戚风蛋糕 或是饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你多烤点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢？沙发要放哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里放沙袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视是放那边吧？你觉得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 来决定规则啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要两个人一起住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就开心的住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么呢？那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜托你去丢垃圾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？谢谢 那我去整理垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗衣服要两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧？两个人的衣服可以一起洗吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜托了哦 我会习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有料理啊 料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有料理啊 料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来煮饭啊 菜就麻烦你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 这是什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待好吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 最喜欢汉堡肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？你好像不是很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成我来造成你的困扰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变得很困扰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很唐突 还请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我很会按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家累不累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你按摩好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚也要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里不行哦 客人要另外算钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？想要我摸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法 那我来按摩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以脱掉内裤？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就能每天很恩爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是被侵犯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是被侵犯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以接吻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也帮你舔乳头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从肉棒好像流出什么东西来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.20,0:25:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.20,0:25:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚买的沙发！！面纸面纸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.22,0:25:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.22,0:25:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 抱歉 面纸……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.23,0:25:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面纸……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.24,0:25:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.20,0:26:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.27,0:26:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想到沙发 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.21,0:26:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.21,0:26:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的才重要 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.15,0:26:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 比沙发还要喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比沙发？ 最爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.17,0:27:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有同居第一次知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.27,0:27:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的睡相很差
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.24,0:28:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.31,0:28:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚放上来了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.26,0:28:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡相不好的？才没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.20,0:28:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气好好 想再多睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.21,0:28:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校？我今天下午才有课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.29,0:28:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的课是 英语
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.30,0:29:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.24,0:29:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再睡一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.27,0:29:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.22,0:29:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.22,0:30:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作？ 一下没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.17,0:30:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.25,0:30:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以脱掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.19,0:30:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.19,0:30:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.20,0:30:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很色的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.28,0:31:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.19,0:31:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.20,0:31:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸吗？好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想舔了 可以舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.22,0:32:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.18,0:32:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.22,0:33:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.22,0:33:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.23,0:33:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.25,0:33:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.27,0:34:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.24,0:34:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流鼻水了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.17,0:34:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸这里的话会很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.19,0:34:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.27,0:35:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以摸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被戳的感觉很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.28,0:36:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.22,0:36:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.23,0:36:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很色的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.17,0:36:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色鬼  这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.25,0:37:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.27,0:37:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.23,0:37:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.25,0:38:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看吗？ 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.28,0:38:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不重吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.27,0:39:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.26,0:40:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽哦
