Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.24,1:53:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？喜欢敏感的地方？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.18,1:53:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你来摸很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.25,1:53:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要我用胸部夹吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.27,1:54:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 我要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.29,1:54:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样有做到吗？没做到哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.29,1:54:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好伤心 好了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.16,1:54:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.24,1:54:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没夹住 好伤心
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.18,1:54:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.25,1:54:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要胸部啊 再有10个就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.26,1:55:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.20,1:55:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么小啊？好伤心
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.20,1:55:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.21,1:55:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是把我当成笨蛋吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.28,1:55:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想说我没胸部对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.22,1:55:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事的？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.17,1:55:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为胸部不太够啊 我用嘴做
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.19,1:56:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.26,1:56:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.29,1:56:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.19,1:57:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.28,1:57:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有变厉害吗？好开心
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.25,1:58:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.20,1:59:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部含进去的？不晓得啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.27,1:59:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概我觉得无法全含进来
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.28,1:59:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要动哦
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.16,2:00:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.24,2:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.17,2:00:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太长了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.24,2:00:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.19,2:00:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.26,2:00:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能含到这样
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.29,2:01:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.25,2:01:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.29,2:02:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.25,2:02:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了好多啊 有很爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.26,2:02:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是很长
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.20,2:03:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有干净了吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.16,2:03:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.25,2:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.26,2:03:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天工作要早起吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.20,2:04:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？我大学是下午才开始啊
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.27,2:04:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到下午为止 一起睡吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.21,2:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.16,2:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？礼物？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.17,2:04:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.24,2:04:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是我的生日 好开心
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.25,2:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以打开吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.26,2:05:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心形的项链 好开心
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.19,2:05:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我戴
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.33,2:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我戴
